<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/28954858-nomad"><img alt="Nomad (Marc Dane #1)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1454868395l/28954858._SX98_.jpg" />
